<item>
            <title>[SOLR-1041] dataDir is not set relative to instanceDir </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1041</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;see the mail thread. &lt;a href=&quot;http://markmail.org/thread/ebd7vumj3uyzpyt6&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://markmail.org/thread/ebd7vumj3uyzpyt6&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A recent bug fix has broken the feature. Now it is always relative to current working directory for single core&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12415755">SOLR-1041</key>
            <summary>dataDir is not set relative to instanceDir </summary>
